sentence.text: This study was undertaken to investigate the prevalence of sequence variants in photoreceptor cell maintenance in patients with Leber congenital amaurosis (clathrin coat assembly), early-onset retinal dystrophy (EORD), and autosomal recessive retinitis pigmentosa (arRP); to delineate the ocular phenotypes; and to provide an overview of all published LCA5 variants in an online database.
